    "body": "\u003Ch3 id=\"h_01KD3XF052TXM7DGYC403YTPZN\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color: #434343;\"\u003EIn this article, we will go over setting up an OptiDev app and getting your OptiDev projects onto your digital signs.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/h3\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"e35f6fa58cbf05f548b99c05f24acc6ab\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/undefined#WhatYouNeed\"\u003EWhat You’ll Need\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"ea0bf049e8af625d4bacf85d5699cc935\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/undefined#SettingUp\"\u003ESetting Up an OptiDev App from OptiSigns\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"e32683f40af7cc2884eca3cb9789fc4aa\"\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/undefined#Security\"\u003ESecurity Features\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://www.optidev.ai/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003E\u003Cspan class=\"wysiwyg-underline\"\u003EOptiDev\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E is an AI-powered app builder, capable of creating quick apps for your exact use case. Visual apps, including dashboards, directories, kiosks, and more can be quickly created using your exact specifications, then quickly pushed to your digital signs with OptiSigns.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHere’s how.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Chr\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca name=\"WhatYouNeed\"\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2 id=\"h_01KD3X94AG5HBJM713Y87QP0PB\"\u003EWhat You’ll Need\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"ec532081f36fbfe35af282dab8ef0e129\"\u003EAn OptiSigns account - \u003Ca href=\"https://www.optisigns.com/pricing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EFree Plan \u003C/strong\u003Eor higher\u003C/a\u003E\u003Ca href=\"https://www.optisigns.com/pricing\"\u003E.\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"ebac7f02b1e690a824e3a42ef43955203\"\u003EAn OptiDev account - \u003Ca href=\"https://www.optidev.ai/pricing\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EFree \u003C/strong\u003Efor Public publishing, \u003Cstrong\u003EStandard \u003C/strong\u003Efor Private\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"e700445281b4ed5df24ab469792710834\"\u003EA screen to display your content\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"ece3f8fb0b81ce262eb581ba0d419a92f\"\u003ENote: If using an OptiSigns Free plan, you will want to see our list of \u003Ca href=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/en-us/articles/33940834613139-What-Do-I-Get-With-an-OptiSigns-Free-Plan#Devices\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan class=\"wysiwyg-underline\"\u003EFree Plan Supported Devices\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E \u003C/strong\u003Eto ensure your screen can be used.\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Chr\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca name=\"SettingUp\"\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2 id=\"h_01KD3X94AP04606ZCJ7WPEVPPZ\"\u003ESetting Up an OptiDev App from OptiSigns\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThere are two ways to set up an OptiDev app on OptiSigns.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe first is directly through OptiDev itself. See their article on \u003Ca href=\"https://docs.optidev.ai/features/publish-to-optisigns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan class=\"wysiwyg-underline\"\u003EPublishing to OptiSigns\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E for more on that.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe other is via the OptiDev app. That is what we’ll be covering below.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETo get started, go to \u003Cstrong\u003EAssets → Add Asset → Apps\u003C/strong\u003E.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/47616485594131\" width=\"386\" height=\"263\"\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFind \u003Cstrong\u003EOptiDev \u003C/strong\u003Eon the list of apps:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/47616485596947\" width=\"624\" height=\"247\"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis will open up the \u003Cstrong\u003EOptiDev Configuration \u003C/strong\u003Ewindow. \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/47616485600019\" width=\"624\" height=\"293\"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThere are essentially four elements to this screen:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"e05521de2b60418b9ce961b70ac6126fc\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EName \u003C/strong\u003E- Give your OptiDev asset a name. This is strictly for use in OptiSigns.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"ed44508a842535d37d08ec05ea197bf93\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOptiDev Published URL \u003C/strong\u003E- The URL of your Published OptiDev project. We will explain how to obtain this in a moment.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"ef9bee781b3b7ab4bb9a342280b62def5\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EPreview Window \u003C/strong\u003E- This shows how your OptiDev asset will look when pushed to a screen.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli data-list-item-id=\"ed6cef2fb9b6b5b1bd5e5c4105e009ff7\"\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOrientation Options \u003C/strong\u003E- Change between Landscape and Portrait orientation for the Preview\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFirst, give your asset a name. Then you’ll need to get the Published URL.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETo do this, go to your OptiDev project, then Publish it. You can publish it either Publicly or Privately. Then, click the Live Site link.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/47616515902867\" width=\"317\" height=\"307\"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECopy the URL from the web address bar:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/47616485602707\" width=\"624\" height=\"29\"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPaste the link into the OptiDev Published URL field:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/47616515904147\" width=\"624\" height=\"205\"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cfigure class=\"wysiwyg-table\" style=\"width: 100%;\"\u003E\u003Ctable style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\"\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\n\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\"\u003E\u003Cp class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIMPORTANT\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\n\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1px;\"\u003EOptiDev and OptiSigns are linked through your browser. To ensure your Published Link displays properly, please stay logged in to both OptiDev and OptiSigns through this process. These can be in different tabs.\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\n\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E\u003C/figure\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENow your OptiDev asset should display in the Preview:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https://support.optisigns.com/hc/article_attachments/47616485607315\" width=\"624\" height=\"279\"\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMake any changes and adjustments needed via the Orientation tab, then hit \u003Cstrong\u003ESave.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECongratulations! You’ve successfully created an OptiDev asset.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Chr\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca name=\"Security\"\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch2 id=\"h_01KD3X94AX8W428SY74VW6RQB1\"\u003ESecurity Features\u003C/h2\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOptiSigns and OptiDev share security frameworks, meaning it is possible to publish OptiDev projects to OptiSigns without ever making the project public. To use this feature, you will need a Standard subscription on the OptiDev platform.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ch3 id=\"h_01KD3X94AXM2Y3MB4KETQTD7EQ\"\u003E\u003Cspan style=\"color: #434343;\"\u003EThat’s all!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/h3\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOptiSigns is the leader in \u003Ca href=\"https://www.optisigns.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003E\u003Cspan class=\"wysiwyg-underline\"\u003Edigital signage software\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E. If you have any additional questions, concerns or any feedback about OptiSigns, feel free to reach out to our support team at \u003Ca href=\"mailto:support@optisigns.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003E\u003Cspan class=\"wysiwyg-underline\"\u003Esupport@optisigns.com\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/a\u003E. \u003C/p\u003E"
  }
}